### Medisoft API Testing
### Requires VS Code "REST Client" extension or PyCharm

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api

### 1. Register a Patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "new.patient@test.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "full_name": "Testing User",
    "phone": "01799999999",
    "role": "patient",
    "city": "Dhaka"
}

###

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "new.patient@test.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. View Profile (Uses Session Cookie from Login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile/

###

### 4. View Available Doctors
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors/

###

### 5. View Hospitals
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/

###

### 6. View Medicines
GET {{baseUrl}}/medicines/

###

### 7. Search Blood Donors in Dhaka
GET {{baseUrl}}/blood-donors/?city=Dhaka

###

### 8. View Health Articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles/
